  "detailed_description": "This is a challenging car parking game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGet ready for unlimited gaming pleasure with constantly updated seasons.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe last and most challenging game of the Car Driver series, which has been running since 2011.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou must reach the finish point without crashing your vehicle between difficult platforms.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach section is more challenging and longer than the other.<br />\r\nYou will have to make hundreds of precise maneuvers with your car.<br />\r\nYou must be careful!",
